327180,"uid":201662,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"56975b53e76fc5f1f184bfd17b031342b87108ae","tid":1327180,"uid":170244,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:35:32.000Z","msg":"所吩咐你們的話，你們不可加添，也不可刪減，好叫你們遵守我所吩咐的，就是耶和華─你們神的命令。 申命記 4:2&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n凡我所吩咐的，你們都要謹守遵行，不可加添，也不可刪減。 申命記 12:32&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n他的言語，你不可加添，恐怕他責備你，你就顯為說謊言的。 箴言 30:6&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n我向一切聽見這書上預言的作見證，若有人在這預言上加添什麼，神必將寫在這書上的災禍加在他身上；這書上的預言，若有人刪去什麼，神必從這書上所寫的生命樹和聖城刪去他的分。 啟示錄 22：18~19&nbsp;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:28:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://kwing.christiansonnet.org/courses/theology/c-04.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkwing.christiansonnet.org%2Fcourses%2Ftheology%2Fc-04.htm&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=b5628c86\" target=\"_blank\">https://kwing.christiansonnet.org/courses/theology/c-04.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n隔左2000年，聖經嘅內容仲有98%相似，幾時輪到一個支共政權話改就改"},{"pid":"047c8999fe86ef60e5a1b01ff94b46e37bbb5175","tid":1327180,"uid":210031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:29:42.000Z","msg":"拎呢本喺警察面前讀會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d35f543ce41ee43cf584edb9028627a0955ab03","tid":1327180,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:29:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bed18d646bdd912bf993ec388923447de4207592","tid":1327180,"uid":30830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3607bf74442538a35bddb08036c4a6f91d2f789c","tid":1327180,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:37:51.000Z","msg":"將呢單新聞SHARE比藍絲耶撚唔知有咩反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:31:33.000Z","msg":"佢地可能會話假新聞"},{"pid":"116c737ea9d92d39aaf9d0427102df64ba906ac7","tid":1327180,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:31:47.000Z","msg":"無同你地講笑<br />\n聖經係支那真係禁書黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/93083\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F93083&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=c8df4508\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/93083</a><br />\n許多中國網民研判，當局全面下架聖經，<span style=\"color: red;\">可能將推出聖經中國版，內容經過審查修改，加入中國傳統以及以習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想，達到「基督教中國化」。</span><br />\n三位網店經營者向《BBC中文網》表示，最近自己店裏的聖經被下架。一位不願具名的店主表示，自己在淘寶的網店以前做《聖經》代購且銷售信仰相關商品，但3月初接到提示，開始刪除店內的代購鏈接，「3月30號已經是看到結果了！」該店主稱，網信辦要求各大平台直接刪除有關產品，雖然沒有明確公告，但「如果這個形式你看不懂的話，你的店鋪就不會存在了」。<br />\n香港中文大學崇基學院神學院高級研究員盧龍光強調，網上停售聖經對非基督徒影響很大。他指出，過去十年包括學生在內對基督教感興趣的外界人士大都通過網購獲得聖經，今後教會以外獲得聖經的人估計會「大大減少」。由此可見，中國政府一直在採取措施，以期減少基督教傳播的影響力。"},{"pid":"9d959ecca6171dabbd93b416f6731e426d0f9ae8","tid":1327180,"uid":266100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:31:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53a2316c5c3e5cfd101090795aff7ba9073069c0","tid":1327180,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bed18d646bdd912bf993ec388923447de4207592","tid":1327180,"uid":30830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3607bf74442538a35bddb08036c4a6f91d2f789c","tid":1327180,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:37:51.000Z","msg":"將呢單新聞SHARE比藍絲耶撚唔知有咩反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:31:33.000Z","msg":"佢地可能會話假新聞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:33:17.000Z","msg":"基督教界已經差唔多個個都知<br />\n如果仲話假新聞個D都唔知佢係咪真係信耶穌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9d26bf8b4c91a7f17de2a5fe289724fcee5ec6","tid":1327180,"uid":114032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:33:25.000Z","msg":"與天鬥其樂無窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n毛澤東呢句野喺佢有生之年已經搞到支國生靈塗炭<br />\n維尼家下又跟晒毛嗰套，真係癲撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca846e8e8f36ecca14164d14f21b10298fd26cd5","tid":1327180,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0f80cbefa9052451551fc9b1cd17abb08ace6e","tid":1327180,"uid":161222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:35:13.000Z","msg":"你也是法輪功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f04989c9984f109e185470b7a14085f449d902","tid":1327180,"uid":83853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:36:53.000Z","msg":"幾時有十字軍東征<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99179516060b42627bfe91ac2927157d1f46b4a2","tid":1327180,"uid":41652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:37:14.000Z","msg":"反而覺得班友係度做9 習種"},{"pid":"2f23e1b9b8d56cd322a795e79c45ef463143e6ee","tid":1327180,"uid":221265,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"81b72ac03880bbcae7b4f1d573f945cfbea81751","tid":1327180,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpGxybrq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpGxybrq.jpg&h=75547f9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n習近平領導下的中國政府對宗教展開大規模鎮壓。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n2019-06-20 16:03<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國政府打壓宗教力道加劇，外媒披露，當局除了以武力鎮壓外，更使出「偷樑換柱」手法，用共產黨的意識形態與中國傳統文化取代聖經，企圖從教義基礎上徹底改造基督教，此手法可上溯至納粹時期的德國政權。<br />\n<br />\n屢屢爆料揭露中國人權問題的《寒冬》雜誌刊文指出，當局近期力推「中國特色基督教」，強迫各地基督教神職人員把社會主義核心價值作為講道的重要內容，進而影響信徒接受對黨的認同，進而融入集體宗教活動與日常生活。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，中國政府透過刪除、竄改基督教聖典《聖經》，來達到前述目標，有的地區更直接刪除《十誡》中「不可拜耶和華以外的神」的誡命。據悉，竄改聖經以洗腦人民的作法並非中共所發明，早在納粹時期的德國就曾把「摩西十誡」改為「納粹十二誡」，要求信徒「尊敬你的元首與主人！快樂地為人民工作與犧牲」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，當局現在也加緊對教職人員的「紅色培訓」，課綱包括「黨的十九大精神」、「習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想」、「社會主義核心價值觀」等，力求徹底洗腦第一線神職人員，使其成為黨最忠實的傳聲工具。<br />\n<br />\n搞完維族搞耶撚<br />\n美國仲唔郁鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:39:39.000Z","msg":"其實大陸版好多翻譯書都好興玩依套<br />\n直接刪除一啲佢哋唔like嘅內容<br />\n<br />\n故買書咪貪平買大陸版！"},{"pid":"a8595a91b6759d653e9af5a4b0984b86e7a56462","tid":1327180,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:40:41.000Z","msg":"超越秦王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5b96bdabf6bc0d6f2ba1f58e6be8354467ed4e","tid":1327180,"uid":14433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:41:17.000Z","msg":"支那是文明社會公敵"},{"pid":"d06d5e0e63069fb2576f47b7c4e129fa68c491e4","tid":1327180,"uid":10438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:44:27.000Z","msg":"拜埋習帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca6bbeb1f88bbcc11fb73fe21067a073407bc7d","tid":1327180,"uid":108224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:44:36.000Z","msg":"那殺身體，不能殺靈魂的，不要怕他們；惟有能把身體和靈魂都滅在地獄裡的，正要怕他。（馬太十： 28）<br />\n<br />\n呢句都應該會刪埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2bb78ae015e73a42b089f800e37233a333c8fc","tid":1327180,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:48:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a585cbd0b4741e076f10a34ab6c6d1e35034d491","tid":1327180,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d959ecca6171dabbd93b416f6731e426d0f9ae8","tid":1327180,"uid":266100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81b72ac03880bbcae7b4f1d573f945cfbea81751","tid":1327180,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:22:41.000Z","msg":"